snippet.title: All-Star Fruit Racing (Trailer Full Version) - Early Access Announcement
snippet.description: SAVE THE DATE! All-Star Fruit Racing will be released in Early Access September 4, 2017 on Steam! Check out our page on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/673190/AllStar_Fruit_Racing/! Follow our page on Steam to stay up to date with all the latest news about All-Star Fruit Racing.
